Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Combines the three remaining FMan PCD sub-API prep stubs into one
bisectable commit. The header (include/linux/fsl/fman_pcd.h) and the
Makefile both need all three sub-APIs simultaneously: the Makefile
references the new .o files together, and the header forward declares
struct fman_pcd_manip (used by struct fman_pcd_action.manipulate.manip)
and struct fman_pcd_replic_group (used by struct fman_pcd_action.
replicate.group), so splitting into three separate prep commits would
leave intermediate revisions with broken header references or Makefile
references to missing .c sources.

Files added (all in drivers/net/ethernet/freescale/fman/):
  fman_pcd_manip.c   (89 LOC) - PR14d-prep, header manipulation stubs
  fman_pcd_plcr.c    (115 LOC) - PR14e-prep, policer profile stubs
  fman_pcd_replic.c  (84 LOC) - PR14f-prep, frame replicator stubs
  fman_pcd_prs.c     (60 LOC) - PR14f-prep, FMan parser config stub

Files extended:
  drivers/net/ethernet/freescale/fman/Makefile - adds the four new
    fman_pcd_*.o files to fsl_dpaa_fman-$(CONFIG_FSL_FMAN_PCD)
  include/linux/fsl/fman_pcd.h - adds ~300 LOC of public ABI:
    * enum fman_pcd_manip_type, struct fman_pcd_manip_params tagged
      union (NAT_V4, NAT_V6, VLAN_PUSH, VLAN_POP, TTL_DEC)
    * enum fman_pcd_plcr_color_mode, struct fman_pcd_plcr_params
      (CIR / CBS / EIR / EBS + color awareness per RFC 4115)
    * struct fman_pcd_replic_member (egress FQID per replicator member)
    * 8 function prototypes covering all three sub-APIs

All 8 new public entry points return ERR_PTR(-EOPNOTSUPP) /
-EOPNOTSUPP / NULL-safe-no-op until the corresponding body PRs land.

Acceptance:
  - Native ARM64 build (make ARCH=arm64 -j32 Image modules on Cobalt
    100, FSL_FMAN_PCD=y, FSL_FMAN=y, FSL_DPAA=y, FSL_DPAA_ETH=y):
    zero warnings, zero errors.
  - All 8 new fman_pcd_* symbols present in System.map as T entries
    with corresponding __ksymtab_* rodata entries.

Body PRs queued:
  PR14d-body - real manip template MURAM programming per RM 8.7.5
  PR14e-body - real trTCM profile MURAM programming per RM 8.7.6
  PR14f-body - real replicator-group + parser HXS programming per
               RM 8.7.7 / 8.7.2

Provenance (v1.1): all four .c files authored from LS1046A RM
only; archived SDK fm_manip.c / fm_plcr.c / fm_replic.c / fm_prs.c +
fman_prs.c at mihakralj/kernel-ls1046a-build@464df181 are read-only
silicon-fact cross-references per spec sec 16 (provenance discipline
risk #12).  No code or struct layouts are copied.

Signed-off-by: Build Cobalt100 <build@cobalt100>
